subject: Football (College)
Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Cyrus Gray and Christine Michael each rushed for two touchdowns and Ryan Tannehill threw for two more scores to help No. 8 Texas A&M beat Southern Methodist, 46-14, in College Station.
